author: JerryRigEverything
description:
This power chair has more high tech sensors than a Tesla! with 2 lidar towers on the front it can drive by itself making sure not to bump into anything as it navigates large crowds. The Strutt EV1 is available right now. Watch the full video for more information!  

And yes - the stunt guy on the back of the chair is none other than the Hacksmith himself! @hacksmith
title: WALL-E is now REAL LIFE
